ARRAY['Codebase-wide context retrieval beyond just the open files', 'Built by Sourcegraph with deep expertise in large-scale code intelligence', 'Free tier includes access to multiple frontier models including Claude', 'Strong in large monorepos and complex enterprise codebases'],
