-- 10. Pieces for Developers
('pieces-for-developers', 'Pieces for Developers', 'AI-powered developer productivity platform for saving, searching, and reusing code snippets',
'Pieces for Developers is an AI-powered productivity layer for developers, focused on capturing, organising, and reusing code snippets and developer context across the entire workflow. The core workflow: when you find a useful code snippet, Pieces captures it with full context - the language, source, related files, tags, and the conversation you were having when you found it. The AI then makes this library searchable by natural language, code similarity, or contextual clues, so finding the right snippet later takes seconds rather than searching through browser bookmarks or code comments. Pieces runs locally on the device with an on-device AI model, meaning your code and snippets never leave the machine. The tool integrates with VS Code, JetBrains, Visual Studio, Chrome, and other developer tools through plugins. Beyond snippet management, Pieces includes a long-term memory feature that tracks developer context across sessions, an AI chat assistant powered by local and cloud models, and workflow activity tracking. The personal free tier is available indefinitely with local storage. Team plans for shared snippet libraries and cloud sync require paid subscriptions.',
